These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, november
3 different games are played: whist, canasta, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, light-blue, turquise
House: tower, townhouse, futuristic
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
City: london, paris, prague
 1. the person traveling to london is the german##1
 2. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes turquise##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is between the italian and the person watching documentary movies##2
 4. the townhouse house is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is the colombian##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the tower house##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Movie-Genre      | documentary    | thriller   | martial-arts           |
| Birthday          | june       | november    | december         |
| Game         | canasta    | mah-jongg  | whist        |
| Color           | yellow | light-blue   | turquise      |
| House   | townhouse        | futuristic    | tower       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| City         | london     | paris | prague |

