The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, entrepreneur, mechanic
 1. the person traveling to miami is the prince-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the fisherman is between the cape-cod house and the townhouse house##2
 5. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the cape-cod house is the person who growslily##1
 7. the person who growsiris is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| House      | townhouse   | colonial    | cape-cod         |
