3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, vegafina, fonseca
3 different games are played: billiard, snooker, domino
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, lilac, chestnut
 1. the person eating kale is the person playing snooker##1
 2. the fonseca-smoker is the pilot##1
 3. the cape-cod house is the person eating peas##1
 4. the wooden house is the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the wooden house is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 7. the fisherman is between the vegafina-smoker and the person traveling to colone##2
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who likes white##1
10. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
