 6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is the tower house##1
 8. the person driving the trike is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the helicopter##2
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

