.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
House: victorian, art-deco, gothic-revival
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, ritmeester, baccarat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, apricot, green
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, engineer, software-developer
3 different games are played: poker, monopoly, backgammon
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, sunflower, aconite
 1. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 2. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes green is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 6. the software-developer is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person who growsaconite is between the victorian house and the person who likes lavender##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growslily##1
10. the software-developer is on the left of the engineer##1
11. the person who growslily is the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | victorian | art-deco      | gothic-revival      |
| Cigar         | bolivar     | ritmeester     | baccarat  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Color   | apricot  | green     | lavender |
| Job           | scientist        | software-developer | engineer     |
| Game         | poker    | backgammon | monopoly   |
| Flower     | sunflower        | aconite        | lily   |

