.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, davidoff, havana
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, russian
House: cottage, modern, townhouse
City: rome, new-york, boston
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, trance, jazz
3 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse, hedgehog
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the russian##1
3. the argentine is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the owner of the lizard is between the fan of reggae and the person traveling to new-york##2
5. the russian is between the person traveling to boston and the townhouse house##2
6. the modern house is on the right of the russian##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
9. the fan of trance is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar      | aristoff      | davidoff      | havana       |
| Nationality          | argentine      | russian    | american   |
| House         | townhouse    | cottage     | modern     |
| City           | new-york    | rome | boston   |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | jazz    | reggae       |
| Pet         | hedgehog | lizard      | mouse    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

