.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, game, cain
3 different games are played: whist, poker, scrabble
House: palace, cottage, wooden
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, october, september
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, black, ivory
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, security-guard, journalist
1. the security-guard is the cottage house##1
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the journalist##1
5. the person playing poker is between the cain-smoker and the palace house##2
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the writer is the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the palace house is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Cigar      | cain       | fonseca     | game         |
| Game          | whist     | poker      | scrabble     |
| House         | cottage | wooden    | palace      |
| Birthday   | may   | october | september    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| Color         | orange     | black | ivory |
| Job     | security-guard     | journalist       | writer    |

