.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
City: marseilles, prague, berlin
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, davidoff, prince
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, december, september
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, balloon-flower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, blues, disco
3 different games are played: poker, chess, whist
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person playing whist is the fan of trance##1
3. the swisher-smoker is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left of the fan of disco##1
6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing whist##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
9. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person eating broccoli and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| City      | prague    | marseilles       | berlin      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Cigar           | davidoff  | swisher | prince    |
| Birthday   | october   | december     | september  |
| Flower           | balloon-flower     | lily        | rose |
| Music-Genre         | blues | trance   | disco  |
| Game     | chess    | whist     | poker      |

 